### Variables (optional - set at top of file)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Get all messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/messages

###

### Get single message
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/messages/1

###

### Create message
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/messages
# Content-Type: application/json

# {
#   "title": "Read 1 Book",
#   "content": "Finish read X by the end of the month",
#   "message_type": "text",
#   "scheduled_date": "2025-11-01T09:00:00"
# }

###

### Get all messages (after create)
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/messages

###

### Update message
# PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/messages/1
# Content-Type: application/json

# {
#   "title": "Updated title"
# }

# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/messages

###

### Delete message
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/messages/2


